---

<section class="about section" id="about">
  <div class="container container--feature">
    <div class="about__grid">
      <div class="about__lead reveal" data-reveal="fade">
        <p class="eyebrow">Why me</p>
        <h2 class="about__headline">
          You&rsquo;ll be working with one person. Me.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="about__body reveal" data-delay="1">
        <p class="about__p">
          I&rsquo;m Josiah. Slate is just me &mdash; no account managers, no
          offshore team, no template farm churning out the same five layouts. When
          you email, I answer. When something needs changing, I change it.
        </p>
        <p class="about__p">
          I started Slate because most small businesses get one of two bad deals:
          a $40-a-month builder that leaves them looking like everyone else, or a
          big agency that quotes five figures and disappears after launch. There
          is a better middle: a real custom site, built well, by someone you can
          actually reach.
        </p>
        <p class="about__p">
          I care about the boring things that make a site good &mdash; speed, the
          way it reads on a cracked phone screen, whether a customer can find your
          number in two seconds. Those are the things that quietly win you the job.
        </p>

        <figure class="about__signature">
          <blockquote>
            If your site isn&rsquo;t the best thing about your business, it should
            at least never be the worst.
          </blockquote>
          <figcaption>&mdash; Josiah, Slate</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about__grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 1rem + 4vw, 4rem);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .about__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1.15fr;
      gap: clamp(3rem, 1rem + 4vw, 6rem);
      align-items: start;
    }
  }

  .about__lead {
    max-width: 22ch;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .about__lead {
      position: sticky;
      top: clamp(6rem, 12vh, 8rem);
      max-width: none;
    }
  }

  .about__headline {
    margin-top: var(--space-16);
  }

  .about__p {
    font-size: var(--fs-body-l);
    color: var(--ink-2);
    max-width: var(--measure);
  }

  .about__p + .about__p {
    margin-top: var(--space-24);
  }

  .about__signature {
    margin: var(--space-48) 0 0;
    padding: var(--space-32);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
    background: var(--paper-2);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md) 0;
  }

  .about__signature blockquote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1.375rem, 1.2rem + 0.9vw, 1.75rem);
    line-height: 1.35;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--ink);
    max-width: 30ch;
  }

  .about__signature figcaption {
    margin-top: var(--space-16);
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink-3);
  }
</style>
